298
00:13:12,305 --> 00:13:16,242
We wanna help you
but you gotta tell us the truth.

299
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:20,645
Guys. Got a minute?

300
00:13:28,142 --> 00:13:30,267
What the hell, Captain?
