308
00:13:51,952 --> 00:13:54,222
Child abusers are generally adept at

309
00:13:54,222 --> 00:13:57,272
manipulating emotions
and shading perceptions.

310
00:13:57,272 --> 00:13:59,428
But in this case,
the abuser had to contend

311
00:13:59,428 --> 00:14:02,641
with two separate social and
familial groups

312
00:14:02,641 --> 00:14:05,434
