tuned social radar.

314
00:14:08,315 --> 00:14:11,288
Well, if he's so finely tuned,
why go after a kid?

315
00:14:11,288 --> 00:14:14,466
It's not about intimacy.
It's about displaced rage.

316
00:14:14,466 --> 00:14:15,719
Rage over what?

317
00:14:15,719 --> 00:14:18,731
Sexual inadequacies,
abuse in his childhood.

318
00:14:18,731 --> 00:14:20,778
So someone with low self-esteem.

319
00:14:20,778 --> 00:14:21,804
Yeah.

320
00:14:21,804 --> 00:14:24,618
But that's where the profile gets tricky.

321
00:14:24,618 --> 00:14:28,541
The same insecurities that drive him
to aberrant behavior in one area

322
00:14:28,541 --> 00:14:31,044
can also drive him to excel in another.

323
00:14:31,044 --> 00:14:35,091
So, he could be, whatever,
head of a Fortune 500 company.

324
00:14:35,091 --> 00:14:37,611
I guess Randall McKenna
moves to the top of the list.

325
00:14:37,611 --> 00:14:39,292
You said he was out of town.

326
00:14:39,292 --> 00:14:41,587
Yeah. Well, I called his office
to schedule an interview.

327
00:14:41,587 --> 00:14:44,850
