395
00:17:28,893 --> 00:17:30,889
You took her to a show on Sunday.

396
00:17:30,889 --> 00:17:33,010
The matinee of The Lion King.

397
00:17:33,010 --> 00:17:34,624
Where did you go after that?

398
00:17:34,624 --> 00:17:36,135
I brought her home to her father.

399
00:17:36,135 --> 00:17:37,576
I don't suppose you have anyone
to corroborate

400
00:17:37,576 --> 00:17:39,881
your whereabouts between
the show and home.

401
00:17:39,881 --> 00:17:40,837
As a matter of fact,

402
00:17:40,837 --> 00:17:43,859
her grandmother joined us
at the theatre and my driver drove us.

403
00:17:43,859 --> 00:17:46,447
Grandma's a regular on these field trips?

404
00:17:46,447 --> 00:17:47,734
She is.

405
00:17:47,734 --> 00:17:49,821
Emily's father's in sync with that?

406
00:17:49,821 --> 00:17:52,098
